SURGEON RECOMMENDATION LETTER

Apollo Hospital, Department of Spine Surgery

Date: 09-Mar-2026

To: Pre-Authorization Department, InsureCo Alpha
Re: Patient Rajesh Kumar (DOB: 12-Apr-1978) | Policy: POL-2024-88321

I am writing to recommend Lumbar Discectomy (CPT 63030) for patient Rajesh Kumar.

Patient presents with severe lumbar disc herniation at L4-L5 confirmed by MRI dated
20-Nov-2023, showing nerve root compression. Despite 6 weeks of intensive physiotherapy
(Feb-Mar 2024) and analgesic management, symptoms persist with a pain score of 7/10.

Procedure is medically necessary to prevent permanent neurological damage.

Signed: Dr. Sharma (MS — Spine Surgery, License: TN-20458)
